title: Metallica - ...and Justice For All (}{eywood Remixes)
description:
Metallica
...and Justice For All
remixes bt }{eywood

Using the tracks available in Rock Band: Metallica I remixed these four tracks.  I tried to make up for all the shortcomings of the original mix, such as being unable to hear the bass at all and everything being mixed really dry.

There are reverb and effects on the drums and the vocals.  Everything was EQd better and the bass track was put up to an audible volume.

Now if only I could do something about that shoebox sounding snare drum (I tried, believe me)

01 Blackened
02 ...And Justice for All
03 One
04 Shortest Straw
